HEADWORD: Trigamist
<hw>Trig"a*mist</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Trigamy</er>.]</ety> <def>One who has been married three times;
also, one who has three husbands or three wives at the same
time.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Trigamous</ent>⟦br⟧
